import * as React from 'react';
import { Button } from 'react-native-web';
import { Header,Container,Title,TitleLeft,HeaderButtonLeft,HeaderButtonRight} from './styles';
import { View,Text} from 'react-native';
import { Entypo } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';


function MealPlannerScreen({navigation}) { 
  return (
    <View>
      <Header>
        <HeaderButtonLeft>
          <Ionicons name="chevron-back" size={20} color="black" />
        </HeaderButtonLeft>
        <HeaderButtonRight>
          <Entypo name="dots-two-horizontal" size={20} color="#1D1617" />
        </HeaderButtonRight>
        <Title>Meal Planner</Title>
      </Header>
      <Container>
      <TitleLeft>Meal Nutritions</TitleLeft>
      <Button
        title="Go to Breakfast"
        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Breakfast')}
      />
      <View style={{position: 'absolute',
        width: 315,
        height: 50,
        left: 30,
        top: 162,
        background: 'red',
        borderRadius: 16}}>
        <Text style={{position: 'absolute',
          width: 85,
          height: 18,
          left: 75,
          top: 178,
          fontFamily: 'Poppins',
          fontStyle: 'normal',
          fontWeight: 400,
          fontSize: 12,
          lineHeight: 18,
          color: '#7B6F72'}}>Hours of sleep
        </Text>
      </View>
      </Container>  
    </View>
  );
}
export default MealPlannerScreen;
